This paper focuses on using image enhancement techniques to improve the effectiveness of convolutional neural networks for image classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of dynamic filter learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning techniques to improve image classification, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of image datasets, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper involves the use of image retrieval techniques, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
